high_descs: Turn around and go to the kitchen counter, to the right of the sink.
Pick up the gold wine glass on the counter top.
Turn to your left and go to the microwave at the end of the counter, on your right.
Place the wine glass in the microwave, heat it up, and remove the wine glass from the microwave.
Turn to your right and go to the refrigerator, across the room.
Place the wine glass in the refrigerator, on the top shelf, to the right of the head of lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm wine glass in the refrigerator.

high_descs: heat the mug and take it out
turn around and head to the fridge
place the mug in the fridge
anns.task_desc: place a hot mug in the fridge

high_descs: Turn to the left and go forward to the counter. Turn to the left.
Go forward to the counter and pick up the wine glass.
Turn to the left and go forward until you reach the wall. Turn right.
Open the microwave and place the wine glass inside. Close the microwave. Open the microwave and remove the wine glass.
Turn right and go forward. Turn right and go forward to the counter. Turn left and go forward to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator and put the wine glass inside. Close the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Move wine glass on counter to the microwave. Move the wine glass from microwave to refrigerator.
